# AFFORDMED ‚Ä¢ URL Shortener (React + Material UI)

A **React-based URL Shortener Web Application** built as part of the Affordmed assignment.  
This app allows users to shorten long URLs, manage redirects, and view analytics (click statistics).  

---

## üöÄ Features

- **URL Shortening**
  - Generate a unique short URL for any valid long URL
  - Store short URLs locally with creation & expiry timestamps
  - Prevent duplicate entries & handle collisions

- **Redirection**
  - Visiting a short URL (`/:code`) redirects to the original long URL
  - Tracks click details: timestamp, source (referrer), and coarse location

- **Analytics Dashboard**
  - View all created short URLs with expiry, creation time, and total clicks
  - Inspect detailed click data for each short link

- **Error Handling**
  - Invalid or malformed URLs show friendly error messages
  - Expired or non-existing codes display appropriate alerts

- **UI/UX**
  - Built entirely with **Material UI (MUI)**
  - Responsive, production-friendly, uncluttered design

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

- **React 18** (Create React App)
- **Material UI (MUI)** for styling
- **React Router DOM** for routing
- **LocalStorage** for client-side persistence
- **nanoid** for unique ID generation
- **date-fns** for date handling

